body:
As you may or may not know, I'm in Washington D.C. now, and I'm not gonna be online for a few weeks (Btw, the Embassy of Australia is right across from my hotel, and I can't help but think about Petlas, Jozz, and Solstice every time I look at it).

But, that's not the point of this thread. It got me to wonder, what are your favorite cities to go to on vacation? Apart from Washington D.C., mine are Boston, Shanghai, and London. So, what're yours?

And, as always, joke replies will be ignored and immediately deleted.
